{"tid":1936803,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果又配合中國政府移除一款加密輸入法","createTime":"2020-03-21T12:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T03:08:44.000Z","uid":134993,"like":62,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8d41146c5e986eb0f095ba577e0cb72fdfadc125","tid":1936803,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://qz.com/1822127/encryption-app-to-avoid-coronavirus-censorship-removed-by-apple-in-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqz.com%2F1822127%2Fencryption-app-to-avoid-coronavirus-censorship-removed-by-apple-in-china%2F&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=0de35570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qz.com/1822127/encryption-app-to-avoid-coronavirus-censorship-removed-by-apple-in-china/</a><br />\n<br />\n腦洞鍵盤是一款聊天加密輸入法。用此輸入法將你的信息加密，不受app的限制，任何只要有輸入框的地方都可以使用。複製密文之後即可自動解密。兼容語音輸入。<br />\n- 火星文加密：把普通的漢字變成火星文，大家都看得懂但是AI無法識別。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------<br />\n<br />\n因為傳出去的訊息是表情符號，中國的聊天軟體難以過濾你的談話，<br />\n結果就被蘋果從中國 APP STORE 下架，<br />\n<br />\n連作者的微信公眾號都被永久封鎖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/huiyuGreyfish/status/1238490170741186560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FhuiyuGreyfish%2Fstatus%2F1238490170741186560&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=0d393cff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FhuiyuGreyfish%2Fstatus%2F1238490170741186560&h=184ccba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/huiyuGreyfish/status/1238490170741186560</a>"},{"pid":"236dff36ad3421dd5d5927b15e14ccf3e2493548","tid":1936803,"uid":66365,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"gay cook good boy<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獎你一塊狗餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4384526ebc3b75783a8ed77285b2b1beaf771103","tid":1936803,"uid":2169